com.gmarciani.gmparser.views

Class AppOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gmarciani.gmparser.views.AppOptions

  • public final class AppOptions
extends java.lang.Object

    This class is a container of all GMParser command line options building blocks.

    Every static features in this class is used by the UiManager to build options entries.
